The Area-12 database and ##00D23C|**ORGANIC DEEPWELL**## are experiencing intermittent data latency in the wake of the **##C40233|SCP-7528##** containment breach. ##FFF3AD|**Should this document's visual elements appear corrupted**##, a simplified version is available **[*/scp-7528/offset/1 here]**.
