[[span class="st"]]SPECIAL CONTAINMENT PROCEDURES:[[/span]] Should it still exist, **##C40233|SCP-7528##** is tentatively contained within **[*/secure-facility-dossier-area-12 Area-12]**'s intranet and database as ensured by that facility's stringent info-quarantine procedures. All personal electronic devices must be searched extensively for **##C40233|SCP-7528##** contamination when personnel exit or re-enter the facility, regardless of status, role, rank, or security clearance level.

Crius.aic, conscripted artificial Warden of Area-12's ##00D23C|**ORGANIC DEEPWELL**##, is engaged in quantum scouring procedures to ensure a total absence of **##C40233|SCP-7528##** contamination.[[span class="fnnum"]].[[/span]][[span class="fncon"]]Deepwells are hardened computer networks which cannot be compromised by ontokinetic or timeline disruptions, their contents protected from alteration no matter the state of baseline reality.[[/span]]â€‡Foundation-wide access will be restored once said procedures are complete.
